					<description><!--[CDATA[<p-->Randy McKnight makes award-winning barbecue, runs marathons and owns a small business. He puts his heart into everything he does — just not the heart he had when he was born. Randy was among the first 10 heart transplant recipients at Mayo Clinic in Florida, a program that is now marking its 25th anniversary. Watch: […]<p></p>
